OL,3,CIslanders urged to talk about
OL,4,Cstruggles as suicide rates among
OL,5,Chighest in UK
OL,7,FThey said: "It can be as simple as
OL,8,F'look at the view' or' 'have you
OL,9,Fnoticed the primroses out', that's all
OL,10,Fit takes and it can be that act of
OL,11,Fkindness from a mental health point of
OL,12,Fview that makes the difference."JThey
OL,13,Fsay that talking and listening like
OL,14,Fthis has the "power to change lives "
OL,15,Fand that sometimes speaking to a
OL,16,Fstranger creates a "positive ripple
OL,17,Feffect". Jo Cottell from Guernsey Mind
OL,18,Fsaid: "There are lots of people around
OL,19,Fwho can actually help those struggling
OL,20,Fto strike up conversations."
