OL,7,FMary Carre, Guernsey Samaritans added:
OL,8,F"We want people to ring us so much
OL,9,Fearlier, well before they get to a
OL,10,Fcrisis."
OL,12,FAs part of the campaign, men in
OL,13,Fparticular are being encouraged to
OL,14,Ftalk more openly about their feelings.
OL,16,FIan McCathie from Guernsey Men's Shed
OL,17,Fsaid: "Men are very bad at talking
OL,18,Fabout mental wellbeing.
